title: Afghans fight Joe Biden's plan to give $3.5B in assets to 9/11 victims - New York Post
content: Afghans fight Joe Biden's plan to give $3.5B in assets to 9/11 victims  New York Post View Full Coverage on Google News
description: Protesters gathered in Kabul to demonstrate against President Biden’s decision to free up $3.5 billion in frozen Afghan assets to give to the relatives of 9/11 victims.
